{"tid":913381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝安琪露Bra拍MV 張繼聰不介意：我仲性感","createTime":"2018-11-23T11:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T13:14:29.000Z","uid":22609,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"23465bd791c74d5aa38f2bb46de530a636340984","tid":913381,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:03:49.000Z","msg":"謝安琪露Bra拍MV 張繼聰不介意：我仲性感<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y0OQ6b38Pl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY0OQ6b38Pl0&d=AQftnGCaSe8XZIqBl4ISuf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=264b367d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y0OQ6b38Pl0</a><br />\n由 Kuen - 2018-11-23 17:15<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWpDyXd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWpDyXd.png&h=98a4eb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古天樂與謝安琪合唱的新歌《（一個男人）一個女人和浴室》MV近日曝光部分畫面，二人要演出夫妻在浴室中相處的默契，謝安琪在MV中有罕見的大膽演出，她上身除淨黑Bra，再同古天樂咀嘴。謝安琪老公23日出席活動時，表明不介意太太性感演出，他說：「我一早知道，邊有得介意，我仲性感啦，期待個mv出街，因為成個project都好有趣，又有古仔加盟。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到會不會呷醋呢？張繼聰話：「我邊有資格呀？我平時拍埋拍埋都唔少啦。」亦不怕太太被大眾睇蝕，指Kay有尺度，不會太性感，可以接受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyO5dXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyO5dXi.png&h=45dbf9b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古天樂為麥浚龍與謝安琪的年度音樂企劃再踏樂壇，飾演浦銘心的第二任丈夫藍定凌。二人受訪時指出，拍攝時他們都投入到浦銘心與藍定凌的角色，所以大家都無尷尬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drugkCq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrugkCq.png&h=0c1e512f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://news.modia.com.hk/2018/11/23/107426/謝安琪露bra拍mv-張繼聰不介意：我仲性感/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F107426%2F%E8%AC%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%90%AA%E9%9C%B2bra%E6%8B%8Dmv-%E5%BC%B5%E7%B9%BC%E8%81%B0%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%8B%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%B2%E6%80%A7%E6%84%9F%2F&d=AQftnGCaSe8XZIqBl4ISuf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=97faad79\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.modia.com.hk/2018/11/23/107426/謝安琪露bra拍mv-張繼聰不介意：我仲性感/</a>"},{"p